### DataKit API Test Examples
### You can use these with VS Code REST Client extension or convert to curl/Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@authToken = <AUTH_TOKEN_WILL_BE_HERE>

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. User Signup
# @name signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456!",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### 3. User Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456!"
}

### 4. Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. Update User Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Test User",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### 8. Get My Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/my-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Get Remaining Credits
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/credits
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Use Credits (for testing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/use-credits
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10
}

### 11. Calculate Credit Cost
POST {{baseUrl}}/credits/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "modelId": "gpt-4o",
  "inputTokens": 1000,
  "outputTokens": 500
}

### 12. Check Available Credits
POST {{baseUrl}}/credits/check
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estimatedCredits": 5
}

### 13. Get Usage History
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/usage?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14. Get Usage Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 15. AI Chat Completion (DataKit AI)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-ai-provider: openai

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello, this is a test"
    }
  ],
  "max_tokens": 100
}